# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID (e.g. G-XXXXXXXX).
# Optional. When unset, GA is not loaded — so local dev and previews never send
# events. Production gets this value from the VITE_GA_ID GitHub Actions variable
# during the Pages build.
# To test GA locally, copy this file to .env.local and set a real ID.
VITE_GA_ID=
